Class Tokenizer

java.lang.Object
  scanner.AbstractTokenizer
      scanner.Tokenizer
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Iterator
public class Tokenizer
extends AbstractTokenizer

This class is a 'wrapper class' that interfaces the Lexer. It creates and calls the Lexer's functions. It returns only the tokens that are specified and skips everything else
